  },
  {
    "key": "82682f2bc284dd1721e01b255bfe0b0411b85ca79ab6ace1b3baa6073b9f9fee",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_26.png[/img] As the campfire crackles, %minstrel% the minstrel gets up and stands high on his stump. He beats his chest and then points to %deserter%.%SPEECH_ON%Yo, yee man of such fleeting feet, feet that flee before you've been beat! The deserter! Oh, the deserter! A dessert for the deserter! His courage he did curdle, his honor he did hurdle, his manliness he did murder! The deserter!%SPEECH_OFF%In one swift motion the minstrel claps his hands and drops back down onto his seat. He's only there for a moment before %deserter%'s hands are around his neck. The company is an uproar, stuck somewhere between separating the two and succumbing to fits of manic laughter.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_26.png[/img] As the campfire crackles, %minstrel% the minstrel gets up and stands high on his stump. He beats his chest and then points to %deserter%.%SPEECH_ON%Yo, yee man of such fleeting feet, feet that flee before you've been beat! The deserter! Oh, the deserter! A dessert for the deserter! His courage he did curdle, his honor he did hurdle, his manliness he did murder! The deserter!%SPEECH_OFF%In one swift motion the minstrel claps his hands and drops back down onto his seat. He's only there for a moment before %deserter%'s hands are around his neck. The company is an uproar, stuck somewhere between separating the two and succumbing to fits of manic laughter.\""
  }
]